  <brief_title>Combination of Insulin Sensitizer and Leptin as Treatment for the HAART -Induced Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Combination of Insulin Sensitizer and Leptin as Treatment for the HAART -Induced Metabolic Syndrome: A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
